---
import Image from "../components/Image.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout page_title="Home">
	<main data-pagefind-body>
		<h1 hidden>Home</h1>
		<!-- This is for search purposes -->
		<img
			id="waves"
			src="/waves.svg"
			alt="MHS Seals"
			width="900"
			height="224"
		/>
		<!--<img id="seal-1" src="/seal-1.svg" alt="Seal 1" loading="lazy">
		<img id="seal-2" src="/seal-2.svg" alt="Seal 2" loading="lazy">-->
		<div id="post-waves">
			<div class="hero-section">
				<div class="hero-text">
					<p>
						MHS Seals is a student robotics team from James Martin
						High School in Arlington, Texas. Each year we build an
						autonomous boat to participate in the <a class="inline-link" href="https://www.roboboat.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">RoboNation
						RoboBoat competition</a>. Our boats are completely designed,
						built, and programmed by students and must complete a
						wide range of challenges that are designed to test their
						autonomous abilities. We aim to further the study of
						autonomous robotics by providing students with hands-on
						multidisciplinary design experience in artificial
						intelligence, computer vision, navigation, mechanical
						design, electrical systems, and marketing.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="hero-photos">
					<Image
						image="/blog/2025-breakdown/launching-boat.jpg"
						description="Launching the boat"
						showDescription={false}
					/>
					<Image
						image="/blog/2024-competition/2024-competition-1.jpg"
						description="2024 Competition"
						showDescription={false}
					/>
					<Image
						image="/blog/2025-breakdown/working-on-boat-1.jpg"
						description="Working on the boat"
						showDescription={false}
					/>
					<Image
						image="/blog/2025-breakdown/seals-and-inspiration.jpg"
						description="Team with other competitors"
						showDescription={false}
					/>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="hero-section hero-section-secondary">
				<div class="hero-photos hero-photos-secondary">
					<Image
						image="/blog/2024-breakdown/awards.jpg"
						description="Award ceremony"
						showDescription={false}
					/>
					<Image
						image="/blog/2025-breakdown/seals-and-simle.jpg"
						description="Team collaboration"
						showDescription={false}
					/>
					<Image
						image="/blog/2024-competition/2024-competition-3.jpg"
						description="Competition day"
						showDescription={false}
					/>
					<Image
						image="/blog/2025-breakdown/working-on-boat-2.jpg"
						description="Building the boat"
						showDescription={false}
					/>
				</div>
				<div class="hero-text">
					<p>
						As the <strong>only high school team</strong> competing in
						RoboBoat, we compete alongside universities from around the
						world. This unique position pushes us to innovate and perform
						at a collegiate level, proving that age and experience aren't
						barriers to excellence in robotics. Through this experience,
						our team members develop advanced skills in software development,
						electrical engineering, and mechanical design that prepare
						them for careers in robotics and autonomous systems.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="hero-section boat-section">
				<div class="hero-text">
					<p>
						<strong>Blastoise</strong> is our flagship autonomous boat,
						designed and built by upperclassmen. This advanced platform
						showcases our team's most sophisticated engineering, featuring
						custom-designed hull architecture, state-of-the-art sensor
						arrays, and intelligent navigation systems. Blastoise represents
						the culmination of years of refinement and serves as our primary
						competitor in the RoboBoat competition.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="boat-photo">
					<Image
						image="/blastoise-nobg.png"
						description="Blastoise"
						showDescription={false}
						style="grid-column: 1 / -1; height: 400px;"
					/>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="hero-section boat-section">
				<div class="boat-photo">
					<Image
						image="/squirtle-nobg.png"
						description="Squirtle"
						showDescription={false}
						style="grid-column: 1 / -1; height: 400px;"
					/>
				</div>
				<div class="hero-text">
					<p>
						<strong>Squirtle</strong> is our second boat, designed and
						built by underclassmen as a learning platform. This boat gives
						newer team members the opportunity to gain hands-on experience
						in all aspects of autonomous boat design, from mechanical
						fabrication to software development. Through Squirtle, students
						develop the foundational skills they need to contribute to
						future iterations of Blastoise and advance their engineering
						expertise.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="info-sections">
				<a href="/about" class="info-section">
					<img src="/blog/2025-breakdown/froyo-run.jpg" alt="The Team" />
					<div class="info-content">
						<h2>The Team
							<svg
								class="info-section-icon"
								xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
								height="24px"
								width="24px"
								viewBox="0 -960 960 960"
								fill="currentColor"
								aria-hidden="true"
								focusable="false"
							>
								<path d="M200-120q-33 0-56.5-23.5T120-200v-560q0-33 23.5-56.5T200-840h280v80H200v560h560v-280h80v280q0 33-23.5 56.5T760-120H200Zm188-212-56-56 372-372H560v-80h280v280h-80v-144L388-332Z" />
							</svg>
						</h2>
						<p>
							MHS Seals has members across many different skill
							levels and interests. We are organized into several
							departments: Computer Science, Electrical,
							Engineering, and Marketing. Each department works
							together to design, build, and compete with our
							autonomous boats.
						</p>
					</div>
				</a>

				<a href="/blog" class="info-section">
					<img src="/blog/2025-breakdown/bruce-with-new-wifi.jpg" alt="Competition" />
					<div class="info-content">
						<h2>Competition
							<svg
								class="info-section-icon"
								xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
								height="24px"
								width="24px"
								viewBox="0 -960 960 960"
								fill="currentColor"
								aria-hidden="true"
								focusable="false"
							>
								<path d="M200-120q-33 0-56.5-23.5T120-200v-560q0-33 23.5-56.5T200-840h280v80H200v560h560v-280h80v280q0 33-23.5 56.5T760-120H200Zm188-212-56-56 372-372H560v-80h280v280h-80v-144L388-332Z" />
							</svg>
						</h2>
						<p>
							The RoboBoat competition is an international
							competition where students design, build, and
							compete with self-driving robotic boats in a series
							of tests aimed at challenging teams through a
							variety of autonomous tasks. We are currently the
							only high school team in the competition.
						</p>
					</div>
				</a>
			</div>
			<iframe
				loading="lazy"
				src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/vPBT0u8P_JE?si=3HLxpSINsJwI-ZWp"
				title="YouTube video player"
				frameborder="0"
				allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
				allowfullscreen></iframe>
		</div>
		<!-- This is the only way to not have these blurry -->
		<img
			id="waves-bottom"
			src="/waves_flipped.svg"
			alt="Waves"
			loading="lazy"
			width="900"
			height="224"
		/>

		<style>
			main {
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: center;
				width: 100%;
				max-width: 100vw;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 3em 0 0 0;
			}

			body {
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
			}

			h1 {
				position: absolute;
				top: 25%;
				left: 50%;
				transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
				font-size: 6em;
			}

			#waves,
			#waves-bottom {
				user-drag: none;
				user-select: none;
				-moz-user-select: none;
				-webkit-user-drag: none;
				-webkit-user-select: none;
				-ms-user-select: none;
			}

			#waves {
				width: 100%;
				border-radius: 0;
				display: block;
				margin-bottom: -1px;
			}

			#seal-1 {
				position: absolute;
				top: 1000px;
				left: 10px;
				height: 500px;
				z-index: 1;
			}

			#seal-2 {
				position: absolute;
				top: 1600px;
				right: 30px;
				height: 500px;
				z-index: 1;
			}

			#post-waves {
				background-color: #375fca;
				color: white;
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				align-items: center;
				width: 100%;
			}

			.hero-section {
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: row;
				gap: 2rem;
				width: 100%;
				max-width: 1400px;
				margin-bottom: 3em;
				align-items: center;
				padding: 0 2rem;
				box-sizing: border-box;
			}

			.hero-section-reverse {
				flex-direction: row-reverse;
			}

			.hero-text {
				flex: 1;
				max-width: 600px;
			}

			.hero-text p {
				color: white;
				font-size: 1.1em;
				line-height: 1.6;
				margin: 0;
			}

			.hero-text .inline-link,
			.hero-text .inline-link:visited {
				color: #b9d9ff;
				text-decoration: underline;
				text-decoration-thickness: 2px;
				text-underline-offset: 3px;
			}

			.hero-text .inline-link:hover {
				color: #e7f3ff;
				text-decoration-color: #b9d9ff;
			}

			.hero-photos {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
				gap: 1rem;
				flex: 1;
			}

			:global(.hero-photos .image) {
				margin-top: 0;
			}

			:global(.hero-photos .image a) {
				display: block;
			}

			:global(.hero-photos .image img) {
				width: 100%;
				height: 200px;
				object-fit: cover;
				border-radius: 8px;
			}

			.boat-photo {
				flex: 1;
				display: flex;
				justify-content: center;
				align-items: center;
			}

			:global(.boat-photo .image) {
				margin-top: 0;
				margin: 0;
				width: 100%;
			}

			:global(.boat-photo .image a) {
				display: block;
			}

			:global(.boat-photo .image img) {
				width: 100%;
				height: 400px;
				object-fit: contain;
				border-radius: 8px;
			}

			.info-sections {
				display: flex;
				justify-content: center;
				gap: 2rem;
				width: 100%;
				max-width: 1400px;
				margin-bottom: 3rem;
				flex-wrap: wrap;
				padding: 0 2rem;
				box-sizing: border-box;
			}

			.info-section {
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				gap: 1rem;
				align-items: flex-start;
				text-decoration: none;
				color: white;
				transition: all 0.2s ease;
				cursor: pointer;
				border-radius: 12px;
				padding: 0.1rem;
				flex: 0 1 calc((min(100%, 1400px) - 4rem) / 3);
			}

			.info-section:hover {
				transform: translateY(-5px);
				background-color: #3c68e0;
				-webkit-box-shadow: 0px 0px 14px 16px #3c68e0;
				box-shadow: 0px 0px 14px 16px #3c68e0;
				color: white;
				text-decoration: none;
			}

			.info-section:visited {
				color: white;
			}

			.info-section:hover h2 {
				text-decoration: underline;
			}

			.info-section img {
				width: 100%;
				height: 250px;
				object-fit: cover;
				border-radius: 8px;
				flex-shrink: 0;
			}

			.info-content {
				flex: 1;
			}

			.info-content h2 {
				margin-top: 0;
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
				color: white;
			}

			.info-section-icon {
				display: inline-block;
				vertical-align: middle;
				margin-left: 0.35em;
			}

			.info-content p {
				color: white;
				margin: 0;
				line-height: 1.6;
			}

			iframe {
				width: 100%;
				max-width: 768px;
				aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
				border-radius: 12px;
				display: block;
				margin: 0 auto;
			}

			#waves-bottom {
				width: 100%;
				border-radius: 0;
				background-color: rgb(var(--gray-lighter));
			}

			@media screen and (max-width: 1100px) {
				.hero-section {
					gap: 1.5rem;
					margin-bottom: 2.5em;
					padding: 0 1.5rem;
				}

				.hero-text {
					max-width: 720px;
				}

				:global(.hero-photos .image img) {
					height: 180px;
				}

				:global(.boat-photo .image img) {
					height: 340px;
				}

				.info-section {
					flex: 0 1 calc((min(100%, 1400px) - 2rem) / 2);
				}
			}

			@media screen and (max-width: 800px) {
				#waves {
					width: 100%;
					content: url("/waves_mobile.svg");
				}

				#waves-bottom {
					width: 100%;
					content: url("/waves_flipped_mobile.svg");
				}

				.hero-section {
					flex-direction: column;
					gap: 1.5rem;
					padding: 0 1rem;
				}

				.hero-photos-secondary {
					display: none;
				}

				.boat-section .boat-photo {
					order: -1;
				}

				.hero-text p {
					font-size: 1em;
				}

				.hero-photos {
					grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
					max-width: 600px;
					width: 100%;
					margin: 0 auto;
				}

				:global(.hero-photos .image img) {
					height: 160px;
				}

				:global(.boat-photo .image img) {
					height: 300px;
				}

				#intro-text {
					font-size: 1em;
					margin-bottom: 2em;
				}

				.info-sections {
					gap: 1.25rem;
					padding: 0 1rem;
				}

				.info-section {
					flex-direction: column;
					gap: 1rem;
					flex: 1 1 100%;
				}

				.info-section img {
					width: 100%;
					height: auto;
					max-width: 520px;
					align-self: center;
				}

				#roboboat-team {
					width: 95%;
					justify-content: center;
				}

				#roboboat-team img {
					height: 4rem;
				}

				#roboboat-team h2 {
					height: 1rem;
					font-size: 1.5rem;
				}

				.departments {
					flex-wrap: wrap;
					width: 95%;
				}

				.departments a {
					width: 45%;
				}

				iframe {
					width: calc(100% - 2rem);
				}
			}

			@media screen and (max-width: 520px) {
				.hero-section {
					padding: 0 0.75rem;
				}

				.hero-photos {
					grid-template-columns: 1fr;
					max-width: 420px;
				}

				.hero-photos-secondary {
					display: none;
				}

				:global(.hero-photos .image img) {
					height: 200px;
				}

				:global(.boat-photo .image img) {
					height: 260px;
				}

				.info-sections {
					padding: 0 0.75rem;
				}

				iframe {
					width: calc(100% - 1.5rem);
				}
			}
		</style>
	</main>
</Layout>
